r-review-no-6-of-2011/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n世界無論正財定偏財都冇咁易搵，唔好人云亦云。<br />\n不過自問唔醒目既就唔好行差踏錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n洗黑錢元素：<br />\n<br />\n1. 被告有冇處理過涉案金錢<br />\n<br />\n2. 是否有合理理由相信是「黑錢」<br />\n<br />\n而涉案金錢是否確實是「黑錢」並非構成洗黑錢罪行的元素。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource:  <a href=\"https://www.fstb.gov.hk/fsb/aml/tc/edu-publicity/seminar2016/MSO_EmergingMoneyLaunderingMethodsandTrend.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fstb.gov.hk%2Ffsb%2Faml%2Ftc%2Fedu-publicity%2Fseminar2016%2FMSO_EmergingMoneyLaunderingMethodsandTrend.pdf&d=ah4jksLE9LN9r3P%2BgshA5W6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=2ed2eb8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.fstb.gov.hk/fsb/aml/tc/edu-publicity/seminar2016/MSO_EmergingMoneyLaunderingMethodsandTrend.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"71d9c516650162e07f26e46617d4b3bd91458171","tid":991450,"uid":126621,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T10:00:18.000Z","msg":"之前炒到咁高 每個單位過千萬<br />\n炒一層都賺幾百萬<br />\n你覺得唔洗還？<br />\n呢次樓爆經濟轉差<br />\n一定要跌好撚多先會傷到呢d 炒家<br />\n跌到得返2 3成都唔出奇<br />\n做大簫條<br />\n<br />\n全球經濟繁華盛世左太耐<br />\n一爆 爆到你唔信<br />\n之前仲要印咁多銀紙"},{"pid":"f0eb9ae5f83b2b478ac719a50d7c7f67dc6a3ae8","tid":991450,"uid":8880,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"71d9c516650162e07f26e46617d4b3bd91458171","tid":991450,"uid":126621,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T10:00:18.000Z","msg":"之前炒到咁高 每個單位過千萬<br />\n炒一層都賺幾百萬<br />\n你覺得唔洗還？<br />\n呢次樓爆經濟轉差<br />\n一定要跌好撚多先會傷到呢d 炒家<br />\n跌到得返2 3成都唔出奇<br />\n做大簫條<br />\n<br />\n全球經濟繁華盛世左太耐<br />\n一爆 爆到你唔信<br />\n之前仲要印咁多銀紙"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T10:53:16.000Z","msg":"投資客早年買落 唔會太傷<br />\n呢幾年先買 叫仔女老婆玩首置<br />\n屋企人幾個一齊夾首期<br />\n大跌加經濟唔好 呢批應該有一部份要破產<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}